  <tr>
    <td valign="top" align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="5">
    Theft of Thought</font>&nbsp;<a href="../Subscribe.asp?DID=120588"><font face="Verdana" size="2">[Subscribe to this document]</font></a></td>
    <td valign="top" align="left"><img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/magic.gif" width="216" height="30" align="right">
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td colspan="2">
    <!--<a href="magic.asp?mode=updateform&amp;ID=120588">-->
    <a href="../UserUpdate.asp?ID=120588">
    <small><font face="Verdana"><strong>Add New Info Here</strong></font></small>
    </a>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td valign="top" align="left">
		<font face="verdana" size="2">
		<b>Description:</b> <br>
		This is truly a great spell...steals 346 to 400 mana and gives to self. Doesn't work on pure tank classes, I.E. the mob has to have mana for you to steal. Only other drawback is its long recast time.
		</font>
	 </td>
	 <td rowspan="4" valign="top" align="right">
    
		<table border="1" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
			<tr>
