				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I agree that this spell is awesome in dungeons with spell casters...  Just let groups know to switch tactics, otherwise they tend to kill casters first.<BR>
<BR>
While yes, it takes up a spell slot due to the insane re-cast time, It's not that big a deal.  There are only 2 spells that never leave my mem bar, being tash and mez.  Every other spell is situational.<BR>
<BR>
For the guy who was looking to go to the Hole...  the top is all melee critters.  8(  Great exp, though you need some decent melee youself for the somewhat magic resistant golems.<BR>
<BR>
Alkiera Kerithor<BR>
