			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Okie, I got this spell and now it is hard for me to remember life without it... kinda like how clarity is a necessity even if you are traveling and arent casting at all =P. On the initial cast it drain thier mana and gives me a bub and a half of mana back (roughly). Then you get the dot effect which basically gives you 2 and a half bubs of mana overall for the cost of 25 mana. I dont like hunting in many places now becuase many mobs arent casters. I try to stay away from sol b becuse the only casters there are the dogs and they are all green now. Gotta go to the hole or something. The recast time is a couple min. So you can cast it on about every other mob. I bought mine for 1k becuase the demand is pretty high for this spell. Ok, hope my little blabber helped you in your travels!<BR>
<BR>
Gingerr Ale<BR>
52 Enchanter<BR>
